Interface NervousSystemElement

All Known Subinterfaces:
Astrocyte, Cytokine<T>, Microglia, MoveableNervousSystemElement, Neuron, NeuronGuestElement
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractCytokine, AbstractMoveableNervousSystemElement, AbstractNervousSystemElement, AbstractNeuronGuestElement, DefaultAntiInflammatoryCytokine, DefaultAstrocyte, DefaultMicroglia, DefaultNeuron, DefaultProInflammatoryCytokine, RepastAntiInflammatoryCytokine, RepastAstrocyte, RepastMicroglia, RepastNeuron, RepastNeuronGuestElement, RepastProInflammatoryCytokine
public interface NervousSystemElement
Interface representing an element of the nervous system. It defines the basic properties and behaviors of an element within the nervous system.
